--- cli [feature] ---
ArchkitBin  [C]   : bin/archkit.mjs CLI router — parses argv, sets ARCHKIT_RUN=1, lazy-imports the matching src/commands/* module | User → THIS → *Cmd
GoalCmd     [S]   : src/commands/goal.mjs — CGR goal intake/list/show/complete/abandon over .arch/goals/ | ArchkitBin → THIS → Goals
ResolveCmd  [S]   : src/commands/resolve.mjs (+resolve/*) — warmup, preflight, scaffold, lookup, verify-wiring | ArchkitBin → THIS → Parsers
ReviewCmd   [S]   : src/commands/review.mjs (+review/*) — runs rule checks against staged/working files | ArchkitBin → THIS → Skills
DoctorCmd   [S]   : src/commands/doctor.mjs — load-bearing gauge, aggregates warmup+drift+intent | ArchkitBin → THIS → ResolveCmd,DriftCmd
DriftCmd    [S]   : src/commands/drift.mjs — INDEX↔source consistency findings | ArchkitBin → THIS → Parsers
InitCmd     [C]   : src/commands/init.mjs (+wizard) — scaffolds .arch/ on greenfield repos | ArchkitBin → THIS → Generators
MarketCmd   [S]   : src/commands/market.mjs (+market/*) — search/install community skill packs | ArchkitBin → THIS → Marketplace
BoundaryCmd [S]   : src/commands/boundary.mjs — enforce/propose BAN layering rules | ArchkitBin → THIS → Parsers
DecisionCmd [S]   : src/commands/decisions.mjs — log/search ADRs in .arch/decisions/ | ArchkitBin → THIS → Decisions
---
InitGenerate [U] : src/commands/init-generate.mjs — MCP runner that GENERATES the .arch/ scaffold from structured wizard answers via the shared scaffold-core | McpServer → THIS → Generators
